freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Sensation of a chemical-like smell continued after my checkin yesterday and got worse overnight. I sensed it both as a scent (in my nasal passages) and as a taste (in my mouth). It wasnt severe but it was noticeable. I know that this was produced internally (not just something in the air in my house) because when I woke up overnight with my head under the covers, thats when the sensations were at their most intense.
Sometimes I detect (barely) an odd chemical-like smell for which there is no explanation as to how it could be in my house.
The odd sensation of smell and taste I had the past days has now gone away.
